  "description" : "Modern-day working-class Chu Wange unexpectedly transmigrates into a book, becoming the infamous and ruthless eldest princess of the Great Feng Dynasty. From the very beginning, she faces the desperate situation of being besieged by four top-tier beast-like male protagonists. After awakening her SSS-level mental soothing ability, she uses sincerity and empathy to tame the ferocious beasts who hate her to the bone into clingy and loyal dogs. A sickly and delicate poisonous bird, a gentle mermaid, an arrogant celestial wolf, and a sunny dragon—in public, they are world-destroying killing goddesses; in private, they are adorable little devils vying for attention and affection. The heroine tears apart scheming women, crushes villains, and ultimately ascends to the throne, beginning a sweet and pampering daily life with the four male protagonists.\nsource: bilibili.com/googletranslate",
